  "description": "<p>A superlight, pocket-packable harness for ski touring or mountaineering. It packs down to the size of a tuna can and can be easily tucked into a jacket pocket or small stuff sack. The design is easy to put on when you're wearing crampons or skis, and with colour-coded waist- and leg loops for easy identification. A handy loop on each leg prevents your ice screws from bouncing and clanking around while you're skiing.</p><ul><li>Variable width Dynex webbing is light and durable</li><li>Diaper-style design with speed buckle for easy on and off without having to remove your skis or crampons</li><li>Seamless Infinity Belay Loop reduces wear points</li><li>2 gear loops and 4 ice clipper slots</li><li>Each leg loops features an ice-screw keeper to prevent it from bouncing around</li></ul>",
